Example about how to set up and run debian sid under qemu.

Create img:
===========

qemu-img create sid.img 2G

Install OS:
===========

qemu-system-x86_64 -enable-kvm -hda sid.img -cdrom debian-testing-amd64-netinst.iso -boot d -m 512
qemu-system-x86_64 -enable-kvm -hda sid.img -cdrom debian-testing-amd64-netinst.iso -m 512

Bring up Eth0:
==============

ifup eth0

Install GCC:
============

apt-get install vim git gcc-snapshot build-essential

